tip.text: Seriously! BEST v60 pourover filter new in Bali, and incredible Japanese sweets as well as a good lunch, this is a wonderful charming and secret spot.  I go here all the time when I am in bali.
Great food! Also. The secret spot for spicy food challenges.  If you have a thing for spicy challenges, this place maybe the only place in the world which the spiciest curries.  Go on a Sunday night!
Excellent Pour over filter brew.  Maybe one of the only spots in Geneva, great staff and relaxing outdoor seating.
